        "bbox": [
            20,
            484,
            332,
            508
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "相对湿度 <70% 操作, <80% 储存",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            508,
            310,
            532
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "室内使用,最高海拔 7000英尺(2000米)",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            529,
            277,
            553
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "重量 255g",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            553,
            196,
            577
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "尺寸 150mm x 70mm x 48mm",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            575,
            327,
            599
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "安全认证 室内使用，符合过电压类别I",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            596,
            334,
            622
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "污染级别 2",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            622,
            173,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "电池安装",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            20,
            665,
            97,
            694
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "警告: 为防触电, 打开电池后盖前后，请勿操作仪表并把表笔与电源断开。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            692,
            467,
            720
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 把表笔与仪表断开。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            718,
            159,
            742
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 用螺丝刀拧开电池后盖上的螺母。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            742,
            240,
            766
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3. 正确安装电池，正负极应一致。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            766,
            228,
            789
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4. 盖上电池后盖并拧紧螺丝钉。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            789,
            213,
            816
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "警告: 为防触电,在电池后盖安装和固定之前，请勿操作仪表。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            837,
            393,
            863
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意: 若仪表出现工作不正常，请检测保险丝和电池是否完好以及是否放在正确的位置。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            863,
            468,
            911
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "操作指导",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            90,
            596,
            121
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "数值保持按键HOLD",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            121,
            653,
            145
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "保持键允许仪表固定测量值以供参考：",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            143,
            761,
            169
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 按下“HOLD”键保持读数， 同时出现“HOLD”字符",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            167,
            882,
            193
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 再次按下“DATA HOLD”键 切换至正常操作",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            193,
            826,
            219
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "背光灯键（BACKLIGHT）",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            238,
            689,
            264
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 按下背光灯键开启背光灯。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            264,
            702,
            288
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 再次按背光灯键关闭背光灯。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            288,
            715,
            315
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "警告：小心触电，高压电流十分危险，应小心操作。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            336,
            842,
            362
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 为了节省电池损耗，使用后请将旋钮调至“OFF”档。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            362,
            870,
            386
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 若测量过程中显示屏出现“OL”，表明测量值超出所选档位，应改选更高档。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            384,
            971,
            436
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意:在某些低交直流电压档位内，若表笔与被测物断开，显示屏将出现任意不稳定数值。该现象由高输入灵敏度所致。若接通电路，可读到稳定准确的数值。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            455,
            968,
            532
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "测量非接触交流电压",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            553,
            653,
            579
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "警告: 为了防止电击，请在使用前，确保正确使用此非接触交流电压测电笔。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            579,
            971,
            627
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 让其探头靠近或插入火线的输出插座孔时。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            627,
            806,
            651
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 如果火线带有220V交流电输出，指示灯就会被点亮。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            651,
            868,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意: 如果是零线和火线缠绕在一起时，此时测试要将两线分开，来进行火线与零线的区分。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            699,
            973,
            749
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意: 此非接触交流电压测电笔设计为高度灵敏探测.当遇到静电或其它能带电体时，可能指示灯也会亮起或瞬间闪烁，这属于正常现象。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            747,
            976,
            799
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "直流电压测量",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            818,
            611,
            844
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意：正打开或关闭电源时不要进行此项测量，瞬间的强大电压将损坏仪表。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            844,
            964,
            894
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "数字万用表/中文",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            28,
            124,
            54
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "RS PRO",
        "bbox": [
            443,
            7,
            475,
            62
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "R5 PRO",
        "bbox": [
            522,
            7,
            554,
            62
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "数字万用表/中文",
        "bbox": [
            872,
            28,
            976,
            54
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "4",
        "bbox": [
            21,
            949,
            31,
            968
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "footer",
        "text": "28/09/2017 Version No. 001",
        "bbox": [
            331,
            947,
            487,
            968
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "footer",
        "text": "28/09/2017 Version No. 001",
        "bbox": [
            521,
            947,
            677,
            968
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "5",
        "bbox": [
            966,
            949,
            976,
            968
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 将功能转盘置于V DC的位置。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            90,
            220,
            116
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 将黑色表笔插入负极COM端口，红色表笔插入正极V端口。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            114,
            400,
            138
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3. 将表笔尖端接触被测物,确保极性正确(红色连正极,黑色连负极)。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            138,
            428,
            162
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4. 显示屏上读取电压值。显示屏显示了精确的小数点，数值。若极性颠倒，数值前将显示负号。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            159,
            472,
            207
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "交流电压测量",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            20,
            231,
            110,
            255
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "警告：谨防触电。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            255,
            127,
            279
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若表笔长度不够不能接触到某些240V用具插座的带电部位，则可能出现插座有电而读到的数值却为0的情况。因此若无电压显示，应检查表笔是否接触到了插座内的金属接口。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            279,
            336,
            374
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意：正打开或关闭电源时不要进行此项测量，瞬间的强大电压将损坏仪表。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            393,
            327,
            443
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/3e257858115a629b9112ea2e2c75344a2c2d01f2e6e110ab28d41809719fc433.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            354,
            236,
            473,
            532
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 将功能转盘置于V AC的位置。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            532,
            218,
            558
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 将黑色表笔插入负极COM端口，红色表笔插入正极V端口。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            556,
            400,
            582
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3. 将表笔尖端接触被测物。",
        "bbox": [
            20,
            579,
            186,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4. 显示屏上读取电压值。显示屏显示了精确的小数点，数值和(AC,V等)符号。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            603,
            475,
            649
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在显示屏上读取电压数据。不断重调功能转盘至低交流电压档位获得高分辨率读数。读数由精确的小数点和数值表示。",
        "bbox": [
            18,
            649,
            473,
            699
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "直流电流测量",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            519,
            90,
            610,
            116
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意：在10A情况下测量时间不能超过30秒，否则将可能损坏仪表或表笔。",
        "bbox": [
            517,
            116,
            968,
            143
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/5c3620f3722e921cc135684cb9e2556fcb3b5078422ea2b13d995305285a475e.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            702,
            159,
            791,
            374
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 将黑色表笔插入负极COM端口。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            393,
            729,
            417
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 测量直流200mA 以下的电流,将功能转盘置于最高DC mA档位，并将红色表笔插入mA端口。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            417,
            968,
            463
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3. 测量直流10A时,将功能转盘置于10A档位，并将红色表笔(10A)端口。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            460,
            947,
            486
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4. 断开被测电路的电源。在你想测量电流的位置打开电路绝缘层。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            486,
            914,
            510
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "5. 将黑色表笔接触被测电路的负极，红色表笔接触被测电路正极。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            508,
            914,
            534
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "6. 接通电源。",
        "bbox": [
            521,
            532,
            600,
            556
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "7. 在显示屏上读取读数。进行mA DC测量时,不断重调功能转盘至低mA DC档位获得高分辨率读数.读数由精确的小数点和数值表示。",
        "bbox": [
            519,
            553,
            976,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/700f2fd621e12b986da3c3005440609116189e3f310dfa77e57df5e56c768dd2.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            695,
            658,
            800,
            906
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "7",
        "bbox": [
            966,
            949,
            976,
            968
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
